      "\n  use List.replicate a.length (List.replicate ε.size \"a\" |>.join \",\")\n  constructor\n  · simp\n  constructor\n  · intro a' b' h\n    simp_all [List.mem_replicate, FinEnv.count]\n    <;> aesop\n  · intro h\n    simp_all [List.mem_replicate, FinEnv.count]\n    <;> aesop",
